================================================================================
                           PROJECT DESCRIPTION
================================================================================

Quetzal is a wireless security research and penetration testing firmware
for the NM-CYD-C5 (ESP32-C5-WROOM-1) board. It began as a port of
ESP32-DIV / HaleHound Edition to this new hardware and has continued to
diverge since — see README.md for the current feature set and a full
description of the project.


